practice in a step-by-step way

01:01:58.770 --> 01:02:01.261
in the course of a busy
life, and then how to use it.

01:02:01.261 --> 01:02:02.760
There are separate
chapters on using

01:02:02.760 --> 01:02:05.300
it to work with anxiety,
with depression,

01:02:05.300 --> 01:02:08.740
with interpersonal
challenges, with chronic pain,

01:02:08.740 --> 01:02:11.230
difficulties with aging,
with really a wide variety

01:02:11.230 --> 01:02:14.010
of everyday practice,
everyday problems,

01:02:14.010 --> 01:02:17.030
and you're welcome to
check that out as well.

01:02:17.030 --> 01:02:18.190
So thank you for coming.

